.TH FACEGATE 1 "May 2026" "Facegate 0.3.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
facegate \- native facial authentication for Linux, including automatic screen unlock
.SH SYNOPSIS
.SY facegate
.RI [ --config " PATH" ]
.RI [ COMMAND ]
.YS
